{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d51a923d9f","title":"周恩来就国民党伪造“伍豪等脱离共党启事”一事给毛泽东的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"447a682588","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"d51a923d9f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9d6253c59e","type":"title","text":"周恩来就国民党伪造“伍豪等脱离共党启事”一事给毛泽东的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be3cf09546","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"469c1e5a6c","type":"paragraph","text":"连日因忙于四川和内蒙问题，并同内蒙军区请愿战士分批谈话，直到今天才抽出一天功夫翻阅上海各报，江青同志也于昨日转来各件，现在弄清楚了所谓“伍豪等启事”，就是1932年2月28日的伪造启事，它是先在《新闻报》2月28日登出的。登后，同天，上海临时中央方面就向申报馆设法，结果，《申报》20日、21日登出伪造的启事，22日登了广告处给伍豪先生另一广告启事的拒登回答，大概这是当时所能做到的公开否认伪造启事的办法。我在记忆中，有通过申报馆设法否认的处置，但结果不明，16日午间已向主席这样说了。不过我原来将伪造的伍豪启事记在通缉杀人犯周恩来、赵容（即康生）之前，现在证明是我记错了，查遍1931年顾顺章、向忠发相继叛变后的上海各报，并无另一个所谓伍豪启事，而红卫兵也未发现另一启事。可见在我记忆中的伪造启事和通过申报馆设法的处置，均在我到江西后发生的，所以我只能从电报和来信中知道，也就不全了然了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"614d8bc795","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，把四中全会后与此有关的编为大事记送阅，同时，送上报道最详的上海《时报》1931年11月12月合订本一册，《申报》1932年1月2月合订本两册，请翻阅。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"762301c974","type":"paragraph","text":"此事需否专写一报告，待主席、林彪、康生、江青各同志传阅送上各件后，请再约谈一次，好作定夺。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80fa19462e","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35f1560636","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b108d8522","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日夜","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2955541158","type":"paragraph","text":"附件","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45cdb40842","type":"paragraph","text":"大事记","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79dd5ddac3","type":"paragraph","text":"1931年","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a268db2256","type":"paragraph","text":"1月，中央开六届四中全会","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e986b7c11","type":"paragraph","text":"4月，顾顺章送张国焘、陈昌浩等经武汉入鄂豫皖苏区，顾留汉口被捕，向蒋介石自首。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6267067e43","type":"paragraph","text":"上海当夜得到消息，中央有关机关全部转移。5月，中央决定消灭顾顺章家属10人。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c44e461a0","type":"paragraph","text":"6月，向忠发捕后叛变，处死。有两处机关破坏。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0dfe39668d","type":"paragraph","text":"9月，九·一八沈阳被日寇侵占。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c4160b141","type":"paragraph","text":"11月，特科王世德（老先生）被捕，供出顾顺章家属被消灭。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77b5c8432f","type":"paragraph","text":"11月21日，国民党下令发掘尸身，在法租界姚主教路爱棠村37号，33号，胶济路，武定路、德坊6号，在新闸路，麦特赫斯脱路陈家巷91号，从21日至28日先后掘出男女尸身各8具，共16人。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cb2a89426","type":"paragraph","text":"报上登出的有：","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"157d93e024","type":"paragraph","text":"时报（22日至25日，27日至29日7天）；","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1103ee39d","type":"paragraph","text":"申报（23日至28日6天）；","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6625d5ca3","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻报（22日，24日至29日7天）；","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb84e15eb0","type":"paragraph","text":"时事新报（24日至30日7天）；","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b438226229","type":"paragraph","text":"民国日报（24日至27日4天）。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a98c9ce874","type":"paragraph","text":"登得最详并附照片的为时报。（附一专讯）","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0994bba737","type":"paragraph","text":"11月底至12月初","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cb463f66e","type":"paragraph","text":"顾顺章悬赏缉拿杀人凶手周恩来等紧要启事（全文附）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"688765ac57","type":"paragraph","text":"报上登出的有：","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc2f542c70","type":"paragraph","text":"时报（11月29日至30日，12月1至2日4天）；","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a25676bbee","type":"paragraph","text":"申报（11月29日至30日，12月1日3天）；","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce5c7d2b4c","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻报（11月29日至30日11月1至2日4天）；","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d3107c907","type":"paragraph","text":"时事新报（11月29日至30日，12月1至3日5天）；","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41a2b47e16","type":"paragraph","text":"民国日报（11 月29至30日，12月1至2日4天）。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d49770af6","type":"paragraph","text":"12月上旬周离沪，经汕头，从永定进入中央苏区。在闽西得知12月14日宁都暴动五军团起义成功。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f161b1da76","type":"paragraph","text":"20日左右，周抵瑞金叶坪。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3f3c11e1b","type":"paragraph","text":"1932年","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a93782398a","type":"paragraph","text":"1月，王世德发表叛变声明（全文附）","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2940159205","type":"paragraph","text":"上海登1月11日申报，其他报未见。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7876a3c6d3","type":"paragraph","text":"据报，南京中央日报登1月2日。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1613309dbc","type":"paragraph","text":"1月28日，淞沪抗战。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ddf857c08c","type":"paragraph","text":"2月，18日起至21日，上海报上先后登出敌人伪造的“伍豪等脱离共党启事”（全文附）。号称243人，并无另一姓名，就此一点，断然为敌伪造无疑。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f87004701","type":"paragraph","text":"上海报上登的有：","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1612b7594b","type":"paragraph","text":"新闻报（2月18日，19日）；","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12d33cbe3c","type":"paragraph","text":"申报（2月20日，21日）；","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9582e2c6c","type":"paragraph","text":"时事新报（2月20日，21日）；","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a5189966b","type":"paragraph","text":"时报未登。","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68f4a962b5","type":"paragraph","text":"民国日报未找到。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c05e475508","type":"paragraph","text":"2月22日，申报在广告栏内登出如下启事：","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e57b09146","type":"paragraph","text":"“伍豪先生鉴承于本月18日送来广告启事一则，因福昌床公司否认担保，手续不合，致未刊出。申报馆广告处启。”","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9426a74cd8","type":"paragraph","text":"这种广告处启事，登在广告栏内很少先例，而又在伪造脱党启事登报的同天，当时一望而知是否认脱党启事的，故未能登出。这想是当时党中央所采取的公开否认办法。","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d51a923d9f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}